      <title>欧盟对苹果和谷歌处以 170 亿美元罚款 | 开盘交易 09/10</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-10/eu-fines-apple-google-17b-the-opening-trade-09-10-video</link>
